  "text": "Phyllonorycter and Tuberculatus composition Leaves were collected from trees growing at the scaffolding-system sites in October, 2005, and stored outdoors until almost all of Phyllonorycter larvae grew to pupae. Phyllonorycter pupae were then collected from these leaves and identified to species by pupal exuviae [CITATION_1] .",
